svg.text: Hi! I’m Natasha Adler, the women behind mikito. My mission in life is to present positivity wherever possible. Mikito was a nickname given to me by my significant other, representing my true self. We all like to hide behind a façade or computer screen and mikito was created to be a place where I can authentically be me. It’s a place where I can change the world one design at a time, one project, or person at a time. My success is your success and I truly live by that. One of my favorite quotes that I follow is, throw kindness like confetti. We could all use a little more kindness in this world.
